{"type": "article", "id": 13581, "title": "拉布拉多犬居所", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-17T07:55:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607133849RjNw3SLYPCeczUKQ.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t此前，日本设计大师原研哉在全世界发起了名为“设计：为了爱犬”的展览策划，号召来自世界各地的设计师，建筑师为狗狗设计居所。近日，马岩松发布了作品 “Niku Rug”，由三个手工编织褥垫组成，这个犬居专门为拉布拉多犬打造，因为拉布拉多喜食肉，因此 “Niku Rug” 用了深浅不一的编制来凸显肉的纹理，让拉布拉多爱上这个开放性的小居所。展览于 8 月 8 日至 10 月 11 日期间，在上海喜玛拉雅美术馆展出，感兴趣的不妨去现场看看。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141322x37i5buIt9LPQYZV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141322DiCSZYLTvze3pWnG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261413236D1ixSF2aPYpUfLn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141323omhxFcOTMjGNbeal.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141323j8QbFmYoEVJ3Wn5w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}